@NODE "floppy" "5DL - Floppy Users"




@{i}@{fg highlight}FLOPPY USERS:@{ui}@{fg text}

You  are  permitted  to  make one backup copy of this disk for your own use
only, please do this now and put away the master disk somewhere safe.  When
playing  "BurtonBird"  from  floppy disk the player data and highscores are
automatically saved to the disk.


      @{b}Please write ENABLE the disk so the player scores can be saved!!!@{ub}


@ENDNODE


@NODE "install" "5DL - HD Install"


@{i}@{fg highlight}HD INSTALL:@{ui}@{fg text}


          1. Make an appropriately named drawer on your hard drive.

          2. Copy all the files from the floppy disk into it.
             (NOT the drawers though)

          3. Make sure you have copies of the files from the libs/
             drawer of the floppy in your hard drive libs/ drawer.

          4. Thats it, no assigns are required :)

@ENDNODE


@NODE "controls" "5DL - Controls"


@{i}@{fg highlight}TO PLAY:@{ui}@{fg text}

              * Stick in the disk (write enabled) or click from hard drive.
              * 3 players positions/hi-scores are saved to disk.
              * On title screen goto options to change a player name (or
                set sound etc).
              * On title screen select your player then choose which level
                to start from.


@{i}@{fg highlight}CONTROLS:@{ui}@{fg text}

              * Up - fly.
              * Left/right - change direction (you bounce from walls).
              * Left/right+fire - go faster.
              * Down - stop flying/moving.
              * Down+fire - try to lay an egg.
              * Fire - hold down to turn "psychic" (red) for a few seconds.
                - press to drop an egg.


@{i}@{fg highlight}OBJECT:@{ui}@{fg text}

              * Eat all the good fruit on each level (in the time limit).
              * Black fruit is bad and decreases your time, so avoid.
              * Avoid the baddies.
              * Collect the dropped treasure for extra points.
              * Collect the bonuses: Extra lives and points etc.
                                     Special bonus games.
                                     Pieces of egg shell.
              * Get 4 pieces of egg shell and you can lay an egg which you
                can carry around and drop on baddies to kill them.
              * Obstacles include: One way sliders.
                                   Teleports.
                                   Sticky blocks.
                                   Bonus points.
                                   Etc...


@{i}@{fg highlight}EXIT:@{ui}@{fg text}

             * Hold down "Ctrl-C" on your keyboard.

@ENDNODE


@NODE "tips" "5DL - Tips"


@{i}@{fg highlight}TIPS:@{ui}@{fg text}

         * Turn "psychic" to avoid black fruits and other obstacles.
         * In later levels fruit, obstacles & bonuses may be INVISIBLE!
         * Don't get mad...get even.


@ENDNODE


